{"tid":1370492,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"721包圍中聯辦　警拘一男　涉刑毀、侮辱國徽等三罪","createTime":"2019-07-27T04:22:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-27T04:54:01.000Z","uid":212249,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"bec0a335a0ca3c654a7c91d8bfcc2b12ab4afc2a","tid":1370492,"uid":212249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T04:22:09.000Z","msg":"警方昨日就 7月21日包圍中聯辦事件拘捕一名男子。警方指出，有組織罪案及三合會調查科經深入調查後，昨日下午約 12 時在長沙灣拘捕一名 28 歲姓馮本地男子，涉嫌「刑事毀壞」、「非法集會」及「侮辱國徽」。<br />\n<br />\n警方指出，被捕男子現正被扣留調查，行動仍在進行，不排除有更多人被捕。<br />\n<br />\n7.21 民陣遊行之後，有大批示威者在灣仔終點，自發遊行至中聯辦抗議，有人向國徽投擲雞蛋及撥漆，以及塗鴉牆壁。國務院港澳辦指示威者行徑公然挑戰中央政府權威，絕對不能容忍。中聯辦指，示威者的行為嚴重挑戰「一國兩制」的底線，嚴重挑戰中央權威。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/721%E5%8C%85%E5%9C%8D%E4%B8%AD%E8%81%AF%E8%BE%A6-%E8%AD%A6%E6%8B%98%E4%B8%80%E7%94%B7-%E6%B6%89%E5%88%91%E6%AF%80-%E4%BE%AE%E8%BE%B1%E5%9C%8B%E5%BE%BD%E7%AD%89%E4%B8%89%E7%BD%AA/?fbclid=IwAR12ilU0Z4woj0JNxO31oUctpwT_A1iKbDrYg6VpMyXv-3z7KDZ0Z05ct_k\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F721%25E5%258C%2585%25E5%259C%258D%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E8%2581%25AF%25E8%25BE%25A6-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%258B%2598%25E4%25B8%2580%25E7%2594%25B7-%25E6%25B6%2589%25E5%2588%2591%25E6%25AF%2580-%25E4%25BE%25AE%25E8%25BE%25B1%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25BE%25BD%25E7%25AD%2589%25E4%25B8%2589%25E7%25BD%25AA%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR12ilU0Z4woj0JNxO31oUctpwT_A1iKbDrYg6VpMyXv-3z7KDZ0Z05ct_k&d=P86Nric8SGsb572WK9RGd0trSvVb5AcF94AlmVXjqEc%3D&h=09daca77\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F721%25E5%258C%2585%25E5%259C%258D%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E8%2581%25AF%25E8%25BE%25A6-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%258B%2598%25E4%25B8%2580%25E7%2594%25B7-%25E6%25B6%2589%25E5%2588%2591%25E6%25AF%2580-%25E4%25BE%25AE%25E8%25BE%25B1%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25BE%25BD%25E7%25AD%2589%25E4%25B8%2589%25E7%25BD%25AA%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR12ilU0Z4woj0JNxO31oUctpwT_A1iKbDrYg6VpMyXv-3z7KDZ0Z05ct_k&h=578dde5e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t